doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='ie=edge')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/styleChat.css', type='text/css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/meyer-reset/2.0/reset.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.6.2/css/font-awesome.min.css')
    script(src='/socket.io/socket.io.js')
    script(src='/javascripts/scriptChat.js')
    title Chat
  body
    #frame
      #sidepanel
        #profile
          .wrap
            img#profile-img.online(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/mikeross.png', alt='')
            p #{user.profile.firstName}
        #search
          label(for='')
            i.fa.fa-search(aria-hidden='true')
          input(type='text', placeholder='Search contacts...')
        #contacts
          ul
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/louislitt.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Louis Litt
                  p.preview You just got LITT up, Mike.
            li.contact.active
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/harveyspecter.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Harvey Specter
                  p.preview
                    | Wrong. You take the gun, or you pull out a bigger one. Or, you call their bluff. Or, you do any one of a hundred and forty six other things.
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/rachelzane.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Rachel Zane
                  p.preview I was thinking that we could have chicken tonight, sounds good?
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/donnapaulsen.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Donna Paulsen
                  p.preview Mike, I know everything! I'm Donna..
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/jessicapearson.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Jessica Pearson
                  p.preview Have you finished the draft on the Hinsenburg deal?
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/haroldgunderson.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Harold Gunderson
                  p.preview Thanks Mike! :)
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/danielhardman.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Daniel Hardman
                  p.preview We'll meet again, Mike. Tell Jessica I said 'Hi'.
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status.busy
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/katrinabennett.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Katrina Bennett
                  p.preview I've sent you the files for the Garrett trial.
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/charlesforstman.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Charles Forstman
                  p.preview Mike, this isn't over.
            li.contact
              .wrap
                span.contact-status
                img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/jonathansidwell.png', alt='')
                .meta
                  p.name Jonathan Sidwell
                  p.preview
                    span You:
                    |  That's bullshit. This deal is solid.
        #bottom-bar
          button#addcontact
            i.fa.fa-user-plus.fa-fw(aria-hidden='true')
            span Add contact
          button#settings
            i.fa.fa-cog.fa-fw(aria-hidden='true')
            span Settings
      .content
        .contact-profile
          img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/harveyspecter.png', alt='')
          p Harvey Specter
          .social-media
            i.fa.fa-facebook(aria-hidden='true')
            i.fa.fa-twitter(aria-hidden='true')
            i.fa.fa-instagram(aria-hidden='true')
        .messages
          ul.messageList
            li.sent
              img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/mikeross.png', alt='')
              p
                | How the hell am I supposed to get a jury to believe you when I am not even sure that I do?!
            li.replies
              img(src='http://emilcarlsson.se/assets/harveyspecter.png', alt='')
              p When you're backed against the wall, break the god damn thing down.
        .message-input
          .wrap
            input.messageContent(type='text', placeholder='Write your message...')
            i.fa.fa-paperclip.attachment(aria-hidden='true')
            button.submit(onclick='sendMessage()')
              i.fa.fa-paper-plane(aria-hidden='true')
    
